+/**
+ * WRLD patch: view manager for the iOS continuous-gimbal local camera preview.
+ * Exposes the native component `WRLDCameraPreview` to JS with `streamURL`,
+ * `rotationDeg` and `mirror` props. See WRLDCameraPreviewView for the why.
